@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_riguxm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v1
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.58) - v2) - wp.cos((v2 + 0.15 + v0 + 0.79)))
    tmp = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.11 + tmp + 0.90) / 0.82))
    tmp = 0.95
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.90)))
    data[tid] = v0
